<a id='GBS.PA15.w.1.0.0'></a><p class='gtxt_body' style='font-size:102%;text-indent:1em;' id='para.30.1.0.box.225.626.1299.263.q.60'><span style='font-variant:small-caps;'>Title.</span>&#8212;To the Chief Musician on Neginoth.&#8212;<span style='font-style:italic;'>Another </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>song </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>to </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>be </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>accompanied </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>by </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>stringed </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>instruments. </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>The </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>strain </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>is </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>at </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>one </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>time </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>mournful, </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>and </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>at </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>another </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>softly </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>sweet. </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>It </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>needed </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>the </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>chief </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>musician&#39;s </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>best </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>care </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>to </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>see </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>that </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>the </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>music </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>was </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>expressive </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>of </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>the </span><span style='font-style:italic;'>sentiment. </span>Maschil. <span style='font-style:italic;'>It </span><span style='f